+ #!/usr/bin/env bash
+ set -euo pipefail
+ 
+ ORG="FSU-4221C"
+ PREFIX="isc-4221-fall-2024"
+ 
+ echo "=== Repository Deletion Script ==="
+ echo "Organization: $ORG"
+ echo "Prefix: $PREFIX"
+ echo ""
+ 
+ # Get all repositories with the prefix
+ echo "Fetching repositories to delete..."
+ repos=$(gh repo list "$ORG" --limit 1000 | grep "^$ORG/$PREFIX" | cut -d' ' -f1)
+ 
+ if [[ -z "$repos" ]]; then
+     echo "No repositories found with prefix '$PREFIX'"
+     exit 0
+ fi
+ 
+ # Count repositories
+ repo_count=$(echo "$repos" | wc -l)
+ echo "Found $repo_count repositories to delete:"
+ echo "$repos" | sed 's/^/  /'
+ echo ""
+ 
+ # Confirm deletion
+ echo "⚠️  WARNING: This will permanently delete all $repo_count repositories!"
+ echo "This action cannot be undone."
+ echo ""
+ read -p "Are you sure you want to continue? (yes/no): " confirm
+ 
+ if [[ "$confirm" != "yes" ]]; then
+     echo "Deletion cancelled."
+     exit 0
+ fi
+ 
+ echo ""
+ echo "Starting deletion process..."
+ 
+ # Delete each repository
+ current=0
+ while read -r repo; do
+     [[ -z "$repo" ]] && continue
+     current=$((current + 1))
+     
+     echo "=== Deleting repository $current of $repo_count ==="
+     echo "Repository: $repo"
+     
+     # Delete the repository
+     if gh repo delete "$repo" --yes; then
+         echo "✅ Successfully deleted: $repo"
+     else
+         echo "❌ Failed to delete: $repo"
+     fi
+     
+     echo ""
+     sleep 1  # Small delay to avoid rate limiting
+ done <<< "$repos"
+ 
+ echo "=== Deletion completed ==="
+ echo "Processed $current repositories"
